Game Types and Descriptions
The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild - Action-Adventure title. Developed by Nintendo.
Super Mario Odyssey - Action title. Developed by Nintendo.
Sonic Mania - Action title. Developed by Headcannon and PagodaWest Games.
Arms - Fighting-style title. Developed by Nintendo.
Spla2n - First-person shooter/Multiplayer title. Developed by Nintendo.
Fire Emblem Warriors - Hack-and-slash/Fighting title. Being developed by Koei Tecmo.
Mario Kart 8 Deluxe - Racing/Multiplayer title. Developed by Nintendo.
Project Sonic 2017 - Action title. Being developed by Sonic Team.
Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim - Action/RPG title. Being developed by Bethesda Game Studios.
I Am Setsuna - RPG title. Developed by Tokyo RPG Factory.
Xenoblade Chronicles 2 - Action/RPG title.
Shin Megami Tensei - RPG title.
Stardew Valley - Farming simulator/RPG title.
1-2 Switch - Mini game/Multiplayer title.
